H. Adams &amp; A. 
<bibRefCitation id="806EEAB9FFCEFFA1ACBAB964FD1EF9B7" author="ADAMS H. &amp; ADAMS A." box="[502,646,1547,1573]" pageId="14" pageNumber="97" refId="ref16687" refString="ADAMS H. &amp; ADAMS A. 1858. - The Genera of Recent Mollusca: Arranged According to their Organization. Vol. II. John van Voorst, London, 661 p." type="book" year="1858">Adams, 1858</bibRefCitation>
